<div class="nameAuth">
  <Header
    [title]="headerTitle"
    (onVoted)="back()">
    >
  </Header>
  <div class="tipsMsg" [ngClass]="{active:levelStatus=='1'||certLevel=='C2'}">
    <div class="grayBgBar mt80Rem"></div>
    <div class="conWrap">
      <p>
        {{tipsMsg}}
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!--C1认证div-->
  <div class="authC1" [ngClass]="{active:certLevel=='C0'&&levelStatus=='0'}">
  <!--<div class="authC1 active">-->
    <div class="grayBgBar mt80Rem"></div>
    <div class="tipsArea">
      <p class="keyColor">
        *您已通过实名认证[C0]，您可以申请更高等级的认证[C1]。<br/>
        如实名信息有误，请主动联系客服进行修改以后，再进行C1认证！
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="registBox">
      <form class="regForm">
        <div class="conWrap">
          <div class="inputCtr borderBot">
            <i class="leftIcon reg_name"></i>
            <input class="input right" name="realName" [(ngModel)]="C1Para.realName" placeholder="请输入您的真实姓名" type="text">
          </div>
          <div class="inputCtr borderBot">
            <i class="leftIcon reg_idcard"></i>
            <input class="input right" name="idCard" [(ngModel)]="C1Para.idcard" placeholder="请输入您的身份证号码" type="number">
          </div>
          <div class="inputCtr borderBot getMsgCode">
            <i class="leftIcon reg_vercode"></i>
            <input class="input right" name="msgCode" [(ngModel)]="C1Para.code" placeholder="请输入短信验证码" type="number">
            <div feedButton class="getVerCode" (click)="getMsgCode()" [ngClass]="{disable:!canGetVcode}">
              {{getCodeText}}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>
      <div class="conWrap">
        <div feedButton (click)="submit()" class="regBtn btn keyBtn">
          提交
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tipsArea bgGreen bot">
      <p>温馨提示：</p>
      <p>1.为了保证您的权益，请填写真实的姓名和身份证号码，提交后将不能更改!</p>
      <p>2.每个身份证号码只能绑定一个账号。</p>
      <p>3.实名认证分LV1，LV2，LV3三个等级；C1等级需要提供正确的姓名与证件号码，LV2等级需要您提供正确的证件正反面照片，LV3等级暂未开放；</p>
      <p>4.图片大小不超过1M。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!--C2认证div-->
  <div class="authC2" [ngClass]="{active:levelStatus=='0'&&certLevel=='C1'}">
    <div class="grayBgBar mt80Rem"></div>
    <div class="tipsArea">
      <p class="keyColor">
        *您已通过实名认证[C1]，您可以申请更高等级的认证[C2]。<br/>
        如实名信息有误，请主动联系客服进行修改以后，再进行C2认证！
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="upLoadPicBox">
      <div feedButton class="picItem front">
        <!--(change)="onChangeSelectFile($event)"-->
        <input type="file"  accept="image/png,image/jpg,image/jpeg,image/gif" capture="camera" id="idCard" name="idCard"/>
        <img id="imgFront" [src]="imageUrl||'../../../assets/images/up_idcard_front.png'" alt="">
      </div>
      <div feedButton class="picItem reverse">
        <!--(change)="onChangeSelectFileRvs($event)"-->
        <input type="file"  accept="image/png,image/jpg,image/jpeg,image/gif" capture="camera" id="idCardRvs" name="idCardRvs"/>
        <img id="imgRvs" [src]="imageUrlRvs||'../../../assets/images/up_idcard_reverse.png'" alt="">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div feedButton class="btn keyBtn picUpBtn" (click)="commitCert()">提交</div>
    <div class="tipsArea bgGreen">
      <p>温馨提示：</p>
      <p>1.为了保证您的权益，请填写真实的姓名和身份证号码，提交后将不能更改!</p>
      <p>2.每个身份证号码只能绑定一个账号。</p>
      <p>3.实名认证分LV1，LV2，LV3三个等级；C1等级需要提供正确的姓名与证件号码，LV2等级需要您提供正确的证件正反面照片，LV3等级暂未开放；</p>
      <p>4.图片大小不超过1M。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
